" TODO {{{
" Number List
" :let i=1 | '<,'>g/^/ s//\=i . ". "/ | let i+=1 | nohlsearch
"		or
" Select your lines in visual mode with: V, then type:
" :'<,'>s/^\s*\zs/\=(line('.') - line("'<")+1).'. '
" Which is easy to put in a command:
" command! -nargs=0 -range=% Number <line1>,<line2>s/^\s*\zs/\=(line('.') - <line1>+1).'. '
" }}}
" vim:foldmethod=marker
